---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="News & Events | Saraswati Shiksha Niketan Inter College, Ghaziabad"
	description="Latest news, upcoming events, academic updates, examination notices, and important circulars from Saraswati Shiksha Niketan Inter College, Ghaziabad."
	pubDate={new Date('August 08 2021')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> / <span>News &amp; Events</span></div>
      <h1>News &amp; Events</h1>
      <p>Stay up to date with announcements, upcoming events, examination notices, and school circulars.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="eyebrow">Fresh From Campus</span>
        <h2>Latest News</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <div class="card reveal">
          <span class="badge">Admissions</span>
          <h3 class="mt-lg" style="margin-top:0.8rem;">Admission Window Extended for Nursery–Class 8</h3>
          <p>Limited seats remain available for the 2026-27 academic session. Families are encouraged to submit inquiries before 31 January.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal">
          <span class="badge">Academics</span>
          <h3 class="mt-lg" style="margin-top:0.8rem;">98% Board Result for 2025-26 Session</h3>
          <p>Our Class 10 and 12 students recorded another strong year, with 34 students scoring above 90% aggregate.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal">
          <span class="badge">Achievement</span>
          <h3 class="mt-lg" style="margin-top:0.8rem;">Students Qualify for State Science Olympiad</h3>
          <p>Three students from Class 10 and 11 have qualified for the state-level round of the Science Olympiad.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="eyebrow">Mark Your Calendar</span>
        <h2>Upcoming Events</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-2">
        <div class="event-card reveal"><div class="event-date"><div class="d">02</div><div class="m">Aug</div></div><div><h4>Annual Inter-House Science Exhibition</h4><p>Classes 6-12 present working science models across all four school houses. Parents welcome from 11 AM.</p></div></div>
        <div class="event-card reveal"><div class="event-date"><div class="d">15</div><div class="m">Aug</div></div><div><h4>Independence Day Celebration</h4><p>Flag hoisting, patriotic performances, and felicitation of last year's board toppers.</p></div></div>
        <div class="event-card reveal"><div class="event-date"><div class="d">05</div><div class="m">Sep</div></div><div><h4>Teachers' Day Program</h4><p>Student-led tributes and cultural performances honouring our faculty.</p></div></div>
        <div class="event-card reveal"><div class="event-date"><div class="d">20</div><div class="m">Sep</div></div><div><h4>Half-Yearly Examinations Begin</h4><p>Mid-session assessments for Classes 1 through 12.</p></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head">
        <span class="eyebrow">Academic Updates</span>
        <h2>Examination Notices &amp; Circulars</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-2">
        <div class="card reveal">
          <div class="icon-badge"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.5 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7.5z"/><path d="M14 2v6h6"/><path d="M9 13h6"/><path d="M9 17h6"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Pre-Board Examination Schedule — Class 10 &amp; 12</h3>
          <p>Detailed date sheets for December pre-board examinations have been shared with class teachers and are available at the front office.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal">
          <div class="icon-badge"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M16 2v4"/><path d="M8 2v4"/><path d="M3 10h18"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Winter Vacation Circular</h3>
          <p>School will remain closed from 25 December to 2 January. Holiday homework packets are being distributed by class teachers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal">
          <div class="icon-badge"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Uniform &amp; Book List for New Session</h3>
          <p>Updated uniform guidelines and the class-wise book list for 2026-27 are available at the school office and website.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card reveal">
          <div class="icon-badge"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Parent-Teacher Meeting Schedule</h3>
          <p>Quarterly PTMs are scheduled for the last Saturday of every term. Specific slots will be shared via the class WhatsApp groups.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head center">
        <span class="eyebrow">Traditions We Celebrate</span>
        <h2>Annual Events on Campus</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-4">
        <div class="card reveal text-center"><div class="icon-badge" style="margin-inline:auto;"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 18V5l12-2v13"/><circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3"/><circle cx="18" cy="16" r="3"/></svg></div><h4>Annual Day</h4><p>February</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal text-center"><div class="icon-badge" style="margin-inline:auto;"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M8 21h8"/><path d="M12 17v4"/><path d="M7 4h10v5a5 5 0 0 1-10 0Z"/><path d="M17 5.5h2.5a2 2 0 0 1 0 4H17"/><path d="M7 5.5H4.5a2 2 0 0 0 0 4H7"/></svg></div><h4>Sports Day</h4><p>November</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal text-center"><div class="icon-badge" style="margin-inline:auto;"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 2c0 2.5-2 3-2 6a5 5 0 0 0 10 0c0-3-2-3.5-2-6"/><path d="M5 21h14"/><path d="M12 17v4"/><path d="M8 17h8l-1.5-4h-5Z"/></svg></div><h4>Saraswati Puja</h4><p>January / February</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal text-center"><div class="icon-badge" style="margin-inline:auto;"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10Z"/></svg></div><h4>Independence Day</h4><p>15 August</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
